 If the farmer 'passes' these restrictions successfully, he or she passes to 
 the 'ordering aspect' in judging requirement 8, on which he or she (not numbers-based) 
 (makes small) the cost of owning (material that makes plants grow better). The tree model is this way a separate 
 version of 'maximization subject to restrictions', the common choice princi- 
 
